updateRewards.t.sol
├── when the caller is not the RewardsManager
│   └── it should revert
└── when the caller is the RewardsManager
    ├── given the node has not staked the minimum amount
    │   └── it should not add the amount to the node's pending rewards
    └── given the node has staked the minimum amount
        ├── given staking is paused
        │   └── it should revert
        └── given staking is not paused
            ├── it should emit a {RewardsUpdated} event
            └── it add the amount to the node's pending rewards
